	A movie ticket booking website is crested where users can book movie tickets. This website is not like the traditional movie ticket booking websites. This website suggests movies based on the users preferrances. It displays movies for the user. Tailor made suggestions are made for the user. The website displazys 5 highest grossing movies in town and which are tailor matched for the users preferrances. 
	When the users log in the website, the user is greeted to a colourful homepage which consists of 5 handpicked movies for the user to watch. The user can then select any movie and when the user clicks on the movie he is redirected to the movies homepage which displays details of the movie such as the show times, ticket availability and screen playing in. After choosing a desired show time the user can select the book now option. The user then has to select the number of seats and make payment to receive confirmation about booking.	
